data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Cross-chain protocol Owlto Finance released a product strategy upgrade, aiming to promote the stablecoin multi-chain interoperability infrastructure centered on the stablecoin project USD1 (@worldlibertyfi) supported by the Trump family. The upgrade will focus on three major directions:
1. Realize the full cross-chain circulation of USD1;
2. USD1 holders can stake on any chain and withdraw from any chain, while obtaining cross-chain fees and compound income from other DeFi protocols;
3. After the "Genius Act" is passed, USD1 will become the core relay asset for cross-chain stablecoin exchanges, expanding its ecological application scenarios.
Owlto plans to build cross-chain infrastructure for USD1 and bring a real user base to enhance its on-chain liquidity and stablecoin market competitiveness.
